::Reptilica/Ramulus::

Reptilica sighs, slumping back in the seat.

"Fine, I'll give you the coordinates," he says,  activating his link and 
sending Starscream the coordinates.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus feels his sences activating, opening his eyes in time to hear the 
word 'rock'. He stands up, looking at Brix and Fliq. He grins, looking at 
Fliq's new part-ram body.

"Nice taste, good beast mode," he says, glancing back at the shuttle, "Ok, 
now we're repaired and stranded. I think we should get working on the 
shuttle."
